        Adds a new ban entry.
        Parameters:
        ip - target ip-adress, can be null
        name - target name, can be null.
        uid - target UID, can be null
        timeInSeconds - the duration of the ban, 0 equals permanent
        reason - the reason for the ban
        Returns:
        banid
